item.title: CpGLP1
item.description: Gene Details: Gene ID: Gene Symbol: CpGLP1 Gene Name: germin-like protein 1 Genome: Species: Craterostigma plantagineum Functional Descriptions: The dehydration- and ABA-inducible germin-like protein CpGLP1 from Craterostigma plantagineum has SOD activity and may contribute to cell wall integrity during desiccation.
